WEBVTT

01:35.221 --> 01:37.971
<b></b>June 20

01:37.971 --> 01:39.751
<b>Yes, right.</b>

01:41.061 --> 01:42.951
<b>Yes, of course.</b>

01:42.951 --> 01:44.851
<b>We'll send it over tonight!</b>

01:46.551 --> 01:50.881
<b>Yes, we're truly sorry. 
We hope you'll continue—</b>

01:55.611 --> 02:00.371
<b>Schedule</b>

01:55.611 --> 02:00.371
<b>Name           Destination         Returning By</b>

01:55.611 --> 02:00.371
<b>Chief


Suzuki


Sasaki


Ishida


Watanabe


Itou


Yamamoto


Takahashi


Mori</b>

01:55.611 --> 02:00.371
<b>6/20 - 7/4
Taiwan Business Trip</b>

01:55.611 --> 02:00.371
<b>Rounds</b>

01:55.611 --> 02:00.371
<b>Back at 5 PM</b>

01:55.611 --> 02:00.261
<b><i>Couldn't he have done a smooth handover 
of tasks before leaving on his trip?</i></b>

02:00.261 --> 02:02.501
<b><i>Bye. Hold down the fort.</i></b>

02:02.751 --> 02:04.501
<b>It came out of nowhere.</b>

02:04.501 --> 02:06.641
<b>And he's overseas, to boot.</b>

02:06.641 --> 02:10.871
<b>Sasaki-san, I'm sorry! 
I forgot one of the estimates!</b>

02:10.871 --> 02:13.851
<b>Call the client and let them know first.</b>

02:13.851 --> 02:15.381
<b>Sorry, Sasaki-san!</b>

02:15.631 --> 02:19.281
<b>The Itou-kun who joined us 
this year is AWOL. What do I do?</b>

02:19.281 --> 02:21.921
<b>What? Wasn't he in charge 
of some documents?</b>

02:21.921 --> 02:25.141
<b>That's exactly it. He even 
took them home with him.</b>

02:27.031 --> 02:30.271
<b>Got it. I'll go call on him.</b>

02:30.271 --> 02:31.731
<b>Text me his address.</b>

02:31.731 --> 02:32.881
<b>Will do!</b>

02:41.791 --> 02:44.041
<b></b>Send

02:41.791 --> 02:44.041
<b></b>Estimate...

02:57.551 --> 02:58.801
<b>Oh, crap!</b>

02:58.801 --> 03:00.431
<b></b>Lock


Sleep


Shutdown


Reboot

03:02.011 --> 03:03.041
<b>See you tomorrow.</b>

03:05.031 --> 03:06.811
<b><i>Thank you for your patience.</i></b>

03:07.211 --> 03:12.111
<b><i>The last train for Shimaida is departing 
from platform number 2.</i></b>

03:21.451 --> 03:23.381
<b>Gah.</b>

03:27.461 --> 03:31.461
<b></b>Alarm

03:27.461 --> 03:31.461
<b></b>Snooze

03:27.461 --> 03:30.831
<b></b>Stop

03:38.131 --> 03:40.221
<b></b>June 21

03:48.401 --> 03:49.361
<b>Huh?</b>

03:56.371 --> 03:58.101
<b>Damn it, I'm out.</b>

03:58.491 --> 04:01.241
<b>Genki Trading</b>

04:01.891 --> 04:03.941
<b><i>Today, I need to make an order form,</i></b>

04:03.941 --> 04:07.301
<b><i>go say hi to a new supplier, and then...</i></b>

04:07.301 --> 04:09.621
<b>Excuse me, Sasaki-san.</b>

04:09.891 --> 04:13.191
<b>One of my family members 
just collapsed and got hospitalized...</b>

04:13.191 --> 04:15.991
<b>Oh, it's okay. Go see them.</b>

04:15.991 --> 04:18.451
<b>If you've got any urgent work, 
I'll take care of it.</b>

04:18.451 --> 04:20.821
<b>Thank you so much!</b>

04:20.821 --> 04:23.501
<b>Hello? Yeah, I'll be right there.</b>

04:23.501 --> 04:24.761
<b>Got it.</b>

04:28.911 --> 04:31.661
<b>It's all this. 
I'm sorry to leave it to you.</b>

04:31.661 --> 04:36.271
<b>Sorry, Sasaki-san, that Itou-kun 
isn't here today either.</b>

04:36.271 --> 04:37.411
<b>What do I do?</b>

04:38.751 --> 04:40.151
<b>Sasaki-san?!</b>

04:40.281 --> 04:45.661
<b></b>Alarm

04:40.281 --> 04:45.661
<b></b>Snooze

04:40.281 --> 04:45.161
<b></b>Stop

04:47.661 --> 04:49.661
<b></b>June 22

05:00.541 --> 05:05.901
<b>Sasaki! I can't take this anymore!</b>

05:05.901 --> 05:09.831
<b>You're doing great, man. 
Keep doing what you're doing.</b>

05:09.831 --> 05:10.601
<b>Okay.</b>

05:11.181 --> 05:16.441
<b></b>Alarm

05:11.181 --> 05:16.441
<b></b>Snooze

05:11.181 --> 05:15.101
<b></b>Stop

05:16.981 --> 05:20.321
<b></b>June 23

05:23.071 --> 05:25.571
<b></b>Alarm

05:23.071 --> 05:25.571
<b></b>Snooze

05:23.071 --> 05:25.571
<b></b>Stop

05:26.121 --> 05:29.581
<b></b>June 27

05:32.331 --> 05:34.581
<b></b>Alarm

05:32.331 --> 05:34.581
<b></b>Snooze

05:32.331 --> 05:34.581
<b></b>Stop

05:40.791 --> 05:42.941
<b>I'm back, everyone!</b>

05:42.941 --> 05:46.091
<b>I brought souvenirs. 
Make sure our clients get them.</b>

05:48.721 --> 05:49.631
<b>What's wrong?</b>

05:49.631 --> 05:52.051
<b>Don't tell me you're slacking 
because of the rain!</b>

05:59.961 --> 06:03.821
<b><i>It's finally over... 
The 14 straight workdays of death.</i></b>

06:04.731 --> 06:07.021
<b><i>I somehow got through it.</i></b>

06:07.661 --> 06:10.491
<b><i>What did we do to deserve this?</i></b>

06:16.551 --> 06:19.381
<b><i>And this blasted rain just won't let up.</i></b>

06:25.421 --> 06:26.891
<b>Oh, there you are.</b>

06:27.391 --> 06:28.891
<b>What's up?</b>

06:29.251 --> 06:32.141
<b>Long time no see, Tayama-san.</b>

06:32.581 --> 06:36.141
<b>Are you all out of energy? 
I kinda need you for something.</b>

06:39.141 --> 06:40.681
<b>Sure, if I can be of help.</b>

06:44.181 --> 06:46.531
<b>Hey, teru teru bozu charms 
for good weather.</b>

06:47.071 --> 06:48.991
<b>This takes me back.</b>

06:49.631 --> 06:53.061
<b>The manager hangs them up 
every year during rainy season.</b>

06:53.061 --> 06:57.981
<b>We let kids who visit draw faces on them, 
and we employees draw some, too.</b>

06:57.981 --> 06:59.041
<b>Huh...</b>

06:59.371 --> 07:02.541
<b>I was told to do my share, but...</b>

07:05.881 --> 07:08.101
<b>I get it. I suck at this, don't I?</b>

07:08.101 --> 07:09.051
<b>No...</b>

07:09.301 --> 07:11.821
<b>Take a long, hard look and say that again.</b>

07:11.821 --> 07:15.311
<b>Art is individuality. Art is expression.</b>

07:17.871 --> 07:19.561
<b>There you have it.</b>

07:20.081 --> 07:21.851
<b>Draw some for me, Sasaki-san.</b>

07:24.831 --> 07:26.621
<b>Draw, huh?</b>

07:26.621 --> 07:28.391
<b>Not your strong suit?</b>

07:28.391 --> 07:30.201
<b>Well...</b>

07:30.471 --> 07:33.721
<b><i>I do doodle to keep me awake 
during meetings,</i></b>

07:33.721 --> 07:36.451
<b><i>but I don't know if that can 
truly be called drawing.</i></b>

07:39.911 --> 07:40.911
<b>Done.</b>

07:42.461 --> 07:43.961
<b>Gotooooooou</b>

07:45.711 --> 07:49.721
<b>Why the manager? 
It really looks like her, too.</b>

07:50.861 --> 07:53.221
<b>Man, that's so funny.</b>

07:55.191 --> 07:57.461
<b>I did draw your manager,</b>

08:01.001 --> 08:02.281
<b>so you're next.</b>

08:04.611 --> 08:06.021
<b>Hey, that's cute.</b>

08:06.021 --> 08:08.111
<b>You were really easy to draw.</b>

08:11.491 --> 08:13.521
<b>Must be because you're 
always looking at me.</b>

08:16.871 --> 08:18.751
<b>Guess I'll draw you, too.</b>

08:31.471 --> 08:32.761
<b>Wow, that's good.</b>

08:33.131 --> 08:34.501
<b>What, this?</b>

08:35.111 --> 08:36.141
<b>The cigarette.</b>

08:38.491 --> 08:42.171
<b>I'm pretty fond of rainy days.</b>

08:42.171 --> 08:44.461
<b>The smoke is more visible,</b>

08:44.991 --> 08:48.121
<b>and it even tastes better than usual.</b>

08:49.111 --> 08:51.131
<b>But I've been so busy,</b>

08:51.131 --> 08:54.141
<b>I completely forgot about all that.</b>

08:55.921 --> 08:58.481
<b>It's because I smoke here that I...</b>

08:59.351 --> 09:00.921
<b>I...</b>

09:05.871 --> 09:06.541
<b>Yeah.</b>

09:07.571 --> 09:10.141
<b>Good night, Sasaki-san.</b>

09:29.151 --> 09:32.151
<b></b>Alarm

09:29.151 --> 09:32.151
<b></b>Snooze

09:29.151 --> 09:32.151
<b></b>Stop

09:36.861 --> 09:38.571
<b><i>Damn it.</i></b>

09:38.571 --> 09:40.361
<b><i>I forgot to turn off the alarm.</i></b>

09:40.361 --> 09:43.421
<b><i>I mean, I was so tired, 
I dozed off next to Tayama-san.</i></b>

09:43.421 --> 09:45.171
<b><i>I need to rest all day...</i></b>

09:45.171 --> 09:45.911
<b>Huh?</b>

09:46.421 --> 09:48.921
<b>Proud of ya</b>

09:47.391 --> 09:48.521
<b>The heck?</b>

09:48.921 --> 09:51.051
<b>W-Wait, is this...</b>

09:51.051 --> 09:52.361
<b>Tayama-san?</b>

09:56.481 --> 10:00.251
<b>Tayama-san, this is oil-based ink...</b>

09:59.351 --> 10:03.061
<b></b>July 5





First day off in 15

10:38.971 --> 10:42.101
<b>Proud of ya</b>

10:42.101 --> 10:45.101
<b>24-Hour</b>

10:42.101 --> 10:45.101
<b>Supermarket S</b>

10:45.101 --> 10:48.101
<b>Tanabata Wishes</b>

10:48.101 --> 10:51.111
<b>Staff teru teru bozu
Let's secure good weather
for Tanabata</b>

10:51.111 --> 10:54.111
<b>Well-done Pork Bone Broth
Extra-Large Ramen</b>

11:15.111 --> 11:15.971
<b>Time to eat—</b>

11:15.971 --> 11:20.141
<b>Didn't you say you were 
laying off the ramen for a while?</b>

11:20.751 --> 11:24.141
<b>It's fine. I'll work off what I eat.</b>

11:24.141 --> 11:25.561
<b>You don't say.</b>

11:26.131 --> 11:29.481
<b>I'm sorry to break it to you 
when you're all motivated to work,</b>

11:29.481 --> 11:31.261
<b>but you're getting off early today.</b>

11:31.261 --> 11:36.281
<b>Huh? Tell me that 
<i>before</i> I take my meal break.</b>

11:37.161 --> 11:38.941
<b>Can you blame me?</b>

11:38.941 --> 11:41.921
<b>We're not getting any footfall today. 
I don't want to waste money on pay.</b>

11:41.921 --> 11:45.161
<b>And you're the most flexible 
when it comes to shifts.</b>

11:47.291 --> 11:51.401
<b>Or would you rather stay and help check 
the expiry dates on the frozen foods?</b>

11:51.401 --> 11:53.051
<b>All right, I'll head out.</b>

11:57.701 --> 12:03.301
<b><i>Man, if she'd told me sooner, I could've 
gone to a ramen place on the way home.</i></b>

12:03.861 --> 12:05.411
<b><i>Can't be bothered with makeup.</i></b>

12:05.411 --> 12:08.811
<b><i>I'll just buy some booze, smoke one 
in the back, go home, and sleep.</i></b>

12:09.311 --> 12:11.251
<b><i>Too bad, Sasaki-san.</i></b>

12:11.251 --> 12:14.121
<b><i>Yamada-san won't be here tonight.</i></b>

12:16.581 --> 12:17.821
<b><i>Speak of the devil.</i></b>

12:19.031 --> 12:21.271
<b><i>He got off at a normal time today?</i></b>

12:21.271 --> 12:24.361
<b><i>I could take this chance 
to scare him from behind.</i></b>

12:24.361 --> 12:25.281
<b><i>What's up?</i></b>

12:25.281 --> 12:26.701
<b><i>Whoa!</i></b>

12:27.581 --> 12:30.471
<b><i>But that's old hat by now.</i></b>

12:33.601 --> 12:34.711
<b>Sasaki-san.</b>

12:36.201 --> 12:37.411
<b>Good evening.</b>

12:38.231 --> 12:39.971
<b>Sasaki-san! Your basket!</b>

12:42.061 --> 12:44.101
<b>Sorry about that! Good evening!</b>

12:44.591 --> 12:46.311
<b>Are you okay?</b>

12:46.471 --> 12:47.971
<b>Satisfaction 100%</b>

12:48.221 --> 12:52.721
<b>I-I'm fine. I was just zoning out 
and dropped it.</b>

12:54.731 --> 12:56.061
<b><i>She's in casual clothes?</i></b>

12:56.061 --> 12:59.111
<b><i>Am I allowed to get a pick-me-up 
from Yamada-san out of uniform?</i></b>

12:59.791 --> 13:02.061
<b><i>You know you're not. 
Don't you stare at her.</i></b>

13:02.061 --> 13:04.591
<b><i>Play it natural. 
Everyone has casual clothes.</i></b>

13:04.591 --> 13:06.221
<b><i>Even I wear them!</i></b>

13:06.221 --> 13:07.371
<b>Sasaki-san.</b>

13:08.351 --> 13:10.381
<b>Here you are.</b>

13:17.231 --> 13:18.901
<b>Thank you very much.</b>

13:19.341 --> 13:23.811
<b><i>Jugemu Jugemu Goko-no-Surikire 
Kaijari Suigyo No...</i></b>

13:19.381 --> 13:23.551
<b>Jugemu Jugemu Goko-no-Surikire Kaijari-Suigyo No...</b>

13:22.551 --> 13:26.101
<b>Were you looking at snacks?</b>

13:26.101 --> 13:28.141
<b>Yes, to have with drinks.</b>

13:28.531 --> 13:31.001
<b>Maybe I'll get something, too.</b>

13:31.801 --> 13:34.651
<b>Hey, these cookies are really good.</b>

13:35.191 --> 13:36.721
<b>Is that so?</b>

13:37.021 --> 13:39.531
<b>Oh, they've got a new flavor.</b>

13:40.181 --> 13:44.411
<b>But if I get something sweet, 
I'll also want something savory.</b>

13:44.961 --> 13:46.911
<b>Hmm...</b>

13:46.911 --> 13:47.911
<b>Yamada-san.</b>

13:50.111 --> 13:52.911
<b>You see the three cigarettes here?</b>

13:53.511 --> 13:56.671
<b>Can you assign each 
to one of those snacks?</b>

13:58.221 --> 13:59.281
<b>Okay...</b>

14:00.921 --> 14:01.921
<b>I'm done.</b>

14:02.241 --> 14:03.761
<b>Thank you.</b>

14:06.311 --> 14:07.181
<b>That's the one.</b>

14:07.791 --> 14:11.061
<b>The one that popped out 
is the snack you want.</b>

14:13.401 --> 14:17.331
<b>Oh, sorry. I shouldn't 
be deciding for you.</b>

14:17.331 --> 14:18.561
<b>I'll take it!</b>

14:22.651 --> 14:25.551
<b>Do you use that method often?</b>

14:26.751 --> 14:28.071
<b>I do.</b>

14:28.511 --> 14:31.481
<b>It's more of a superstition for me.</b>

14:32.221 --> 14:35.131
<b>If the first one pops out, 
I'll get to go home early today.</b>

14:35.131 --> 14:37.831
<b>If it's the second one, 
I'll get a day off this week.</b>

14:38.511 --> 14:41.661
<b>And if it's the third one, 
at the register today...</b>

14:45.041 --> 14:46.411
<b>Never mind.</b>

14:46.861 --> 14:48.731
<b>I'm glad you could decide on a snack.</b>

14:49.421 --> 14:51.051
<b>I'll be going now.</b>

14:51.391 --> 14:53.241
<b>Take care on your way home.</b>

14:53.711 --> 14:55.771
<b>I will. You too, Sasaki-san.</b>

15:07.421 --> 15:09.281
<b><i>"And if it's the third one,</i></b>

15:09.281 --> 15:11.881
<b><i>Yamada-san will be 
manning a register today."</i></b>

15:12.301 --> 15:14.861
<b><i>It's obvious even if you cut yourself off,</i></b>

15:14.861 --> 15:16.751
<b><i>Mr. Trying-to-Keep-it-Classy.</i></b>

15:23.841 --> 15:26.361
<b><i>If the third one pops out, he'll realize.</i></b>

15:26.361 --> 15:28.761
<b><i>If it's the second one, he won't.</i></b>

15:29.411 --> 15:31.481
<b><i>And if it's the first...</i></b>

15:42.991 --> 15:47.951
<b>I think that means something bad's 
going to happen to Sasaki-san.</b>

15:54.541 --> 15:56.261
<b><i>I've done it now!</i></b>

15:56.261 --> 15:58.541
<b><i>I was so distracted by 
Yamada-san in casual wear</i></b>

15:58.541 --> 16:00.441
<b><i>that I forgot I had this 
magazine under my arm!</i></b>

16:00.441 --> 16:03.791
<b><i>I took it out without paying for it!</i></b>

16:03.791 --> 16:06.541
<b>Office</b>

16:04.861 --> 16:06.551
<b>Sir.</b>

16:06.901 --> 16:09.211
<b>We take a very dim view of shoplifting.</b>

16:09.211 --> 16:11.691
<b>I'm sorry. I didn't mean to.</b>

16:11.691 --> 16:14.681
<b>Everybody says that, Sasaki-kun.</b>

16:16.181 --> 16:20.221
<b>24-Hour</b>

16:16.181 --> 16:20.221
<b>Supermarket S</b>

16:17.231 --> 16:21.451
<b>I'm truly sorry!</b>

16:23.181 --> 16:26.811
<b>Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b>

16:27.311 --> 16:30.941
<b>Editing & Typesetting: Geoff Mazzolini
Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b>

16:31.651 --> 16:34.901
<b>Quality Check: Zachary Carlysle
Translation Check: Sho Stifler</b>
